\begin_layout Standard
This account easily can knock the legs out from under heterodox criticisms
 of the mainstream.
 Almost by definition, a penumbra of cutting-edge research surrounds an
 obsolete orthodox core, but because heterodox economists are – again, almost
 by definition – absent from institutions where this penumbra is most visible,
 they are unlikely even to be aware of such currents.
